Common.Strapline.Common.Text: BRAND NEW CBD OFFICE SUITE IN AN ICONIC BUILDING

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE, as the exclusive sales agent, is pleased to present 7-9 Wilmot Street, Sydney.

7-9 Wilmot Street, Sydney is a five story freehold building in the heart of the Sydney CBD occupying a land holding of 248sqm*. The property is located conveniently in the centre of Sydney CBD, lending itself to nearby amenities, including iconic Sydney landmarks such as Town Hall, QVB and high-end retail outlets. Public transport is also immediately accessible to the property, with the light rail, Town Hall train station and bus services within a short walking distance.

This property represents an exciting opportunity for discerning purchasers to acquire a freehold property with office and residential development upside. This would see 7-9 Wilmot Street benefit from reaching a potential GFA of 1,984sqm* (STCA).

7-9 Wilmot Street, Sydney benefits from the following key attributes:
- Premium location in the heart of Sydney CBD
- Freehold investment with office and residential development upside (STCA)
- Significant passing income
-Ability to obtain vacant possession within 12 months
- Close proximity to local amenities and public transport, including Light Rail and Town Hall Train Station

7-9 Wilmot Street, Sydney will be made via Public Auction on Tuesday, 3 August 2021 at 10:30am at AuctionWORKS (online bidding available).

For more information or to request access to the due diligence room, please contact the exclusive selling agents.

*Approximate

Note: All financial figures have been provided by the Vendor. Purchasers are advised to conduct their own independent due diligence.
